title: CWTK - Robert's Meat Sauce & Spagetti - Swedish Pasta

media:group.media:title: CWTK - Robert's Meat Sauce & Spagetti - Swedish Pasta
media:group.media:description:
Yes some people make meatsauce and pasta like this in Sweden and it's unironically the best and fastest way to fill your belly up with good sauce. 

800gram minced Beef
2x 2dl Crème fraîche bland or whatever flavor you like
2x Onions or whatever the amount you want
As much Garlic as you want, 5-6 cloves perhaps?
Some concentrated tomato mush.
Soysauce
2.5dl of cream "didnt use all"
Spyeses.
Don't forget ketchup.
and a Glass of Mjölk yum
